singapor exchang plan option contract the singapor intern monetari exchang ltd , simex , said it would launch at least two option on futur contract thi year . simex said in a press releas that the option contract would be base on the currenc and interest rate futur current trade on the exchang and be start `` toward the third quarter . '' simex , which is link to the chicago mercantil exchang , current trade three currenc futur -- on deutsch mark , japanes yen and british pound -- and two interest rate futur -- on u.s. treasury-bond and three-month eurodollar .